{"tid":2403932,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"波多野結衣自爆患顏面神經麻痺 可能隨時變歪嘴","createTime":"2021-02-11T11:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T06:57:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":101,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8f45fb81b5c6a5348aa1eb68773d9090ad76dc","tid":2403932,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M-S55TKC6ZQdSKpukx3Wgn8mCwA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F7BY6R5JDRH45IUVWWJRACMJXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM-S55TKC6ZQdSKpukx3Wgn8mCwA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF7BY6R5JDRH45IUVWWJRACMJXE.jpg&h=47decd9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靠靚樣搵食的AV天后波多野結衣前日在Twitter自爆患上顏面神經麻痺，雖然並不是武漢肺炎或性病，但卻可能對波多野的事業影響更加深遠，事關患者會出現面部肌肉無力及不協調，導致口角和舌頭歪斜，以及口水外流等症狀。<br />\n<br />\n波多野前日表示由於正在接受類固醇治療，令到免疫力下降，所以暫時不能外出，她已經取消了本月20日的活動。波多野昨日又再留言指她習慣忍受痛苦，令自己變得堅強，但當她一個人時卻忍不住喊爆，之後舌頭就開始麻痺，面部亦感到跟昨日不同。其實，近期亦有不少AV迷留言指已經32歲的波多野變臉，懷疑她在臉上動過手腳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IHbWGplwpjOR7-EBm7_J-tePKRM=/802x1003/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JDCGB6IJYVAMJB274CYTAPKXIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIHbWGplwpjOR7-EBm7_J-tePKRM%3D%2F802x1003%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJDCGB6IJYVAMJB274CYTAPKXIE.jpg&h=89daa5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UdEQIJYv1ZbAN2hCxa6iDfyHNyU=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4WKPY7NYOJH2ZGECWONUI2DA7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUdEQIJYv1ZbAN2hCxa6iDfyHNyU%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4WKPY7NYOJH2ZGECWONUI2DA7M.jpg&h=b9797acd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24c8cc62f5f8a6353dec204c4ba7a323fa657504","tid":2403932,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cd402789069656faeb15578c28d36cc3e1c7f4","tid":2403932,"uid":7043,"like":225,"dislike":10,"score":215,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"可能平時含撚用錯力傷到d面部肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6da0b4689008dbd0386d481b4f4e011013d6e9","tid":2403932,"uid":389053,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7be38fc1aa2a72df9f43f9104f44579cf28af1ae","tid":2403932,"uid":74622,"like":55,"dislike":9,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"就算係班人懷疑啲乜<br />\n懷疑人哋整過容好咩<br />\n打返你個飛機啦"},{"pid":"3d49d32a43499aa8809358c0b35efcd84d8dc2c5","tid":2403932,"uid":183301,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"呢兩張完全唔同左樣既"},{"pid":"456a45a1b95821fbc78f345e6d973813d2dd6d7a","tid":2403932,"uid":261849,"like":17,"dislike":22,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:40:46.000Z","msg":"求其啦....都唔睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2f8f390cea7eca3759d351210e23339a32312c","tid":2403932,"uid":16659,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"44cd402789069656faeb15578c28d36cc3e1c7f4","tid":2403932,"uid":7043,"like":225,"dislike":10,"score":215,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"可能平時含撚用錯力傷到d面部肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"re